item.description: × CLINT HD Wallpaper ❮ ❯ No one knows where he comes from or why he fights, but everyone born in the Wastelands knows that he is the only semblance of justice in these parts. With his lightning reflexes and unparalleled accuracy, a flurry of bullets would be buried in his enemies' foreheads before they had time to blink.
